data.description: Stunning, very well-maintained two-story home in desirable Sweetwater Community located in the Texas Hill Country has it all! This 5-bedroom 3.5-bathroom home sits on a corner lot with no direct neighbors on either side and behind property. As you enter the home, you’re greeted by the 12' ceiling wide open floor plan that enhances the abundance of natural light. Large foyer with trey ceiling, family room, dining area, gourmet kitchen with huge island is great for hosting family and friends. Don't forget the study/flex room with trey ceiling that can be used as you’d like. First floor also includes 2 bedrooms, a full and a half bath, and the laundry room.  Don't forget the owner’s suite that features windows with a backyard and that hill country view. The ensuite has 2 vanities - one with vanity seating area, large shower with bench, stand-alone garden tub, and large walk-in closet. Upstairs there is a game room, 2 bedrooms with walk-in closets, an additional walk-in closet at game room, and an expanded full bath with double vanity. The three-sided covered patio with ceiling fan has great views of the hill country. This home boasts a multitude of upgrades including a wood accent wall and light fixtures that complement the look as you enter the home, wood-look laminate flooring in the main living areas, quartz countertops, gas cooktop, built-in double electric ovens, blinds, remote control shade for primary bath window, additional cabinets in laundry and bathrooms, ceiling fans in all bedrooms, interior insulated walls for enhanced comfort, video doorbell, security cameras, and a whole house water filtration system. As a resident of the Sweetwater Community, you’ll enjoy access to many amenities such as two resort-style pools, splash pad, fitness center and many more.
